Student management system

1.principle
add Faculty 
remove Faculty 
update Faculty info 
generate report 
assign role to Faculty


2.Faculty
add/remove student 
generate timetable
arrange exam
update score
attendence 


3. Student 
view/update personal info
view report
access exam
view time table
payment of fees (Then seat allocation)


exam score is updated atomatically in scoreboard table

seat allocation 
roll no. generates (auto increment)
